      "raw_text": "SALT LAKE, Utah, May 49,\nThe Oregon Short Line headquart-\ners announce that the Northwest\nern company has purchased the old\nright of way Of the Northwestern\ncompany and that engineers are\nnow In the field. Preliminary to\nthe immediate construction of a\nline from Huntington, Ore, to Lew\niston, Idaho, w. H. Bancroft, gen.\neral manager Of the Oregon Short\nLine, was elected president of the\nnew company. 1t is understood\nthat a new feeder is being built\nto offset the invasion OF Hill In the\nHartman territory."
